HEADWORD: Frugivora
<hw>Fru*giv"o*ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Frugivorous</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The fruit bate; a
